OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Daniel Boal
OL,8,FAs we enter day 12 of the US and
OL,9,FIsrael's war with Iran, hundreds of
OL,10,Fthousands of people have already been
OL,11,Fdisplaced, and more than 1,700 have
OL,12,Fbeen killed across the region.
OL,14,FThe humanitarian toll continues to
OL,15,Fmount as US President Donald Trump and
OL,16,Fhis administration give conflicting
OL,17,Fmessages over just how long the war
OL,18,Fwill go on, with Iran stating they're
OL,19,Fprepared for a long fight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
