CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FWith no immediate end in sight,
OL,7,Fjournalists around the world are
OL,8,Fscrambling for details to accurately
OL,9,Ftell the stories in the Middle East
OL,10,Fand Iran.
OL,12,FITV News breaks down how and why you
OL,13,Fmay be seeing more footage, detail,
OL,14,Fand newslines coming from certain
OL,15,Fcountries, both in the Middle East and
OL,16,Fbeyond - even though at this point,
OL,17,Fsome 17 nations are involved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
