OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIsrael and the US launched joint
OL,7,Fattacks on Iran on Saturday, February
OL,8,F28. Supreme Leader Ali Khamenei was
OL,9,Fkilled during the initial strikes,
OL,10,Ftriggering a robust response from
OL,11,FTehran.
OL,13,FIran fired retaliatory strikes towards
OL,14,FIsrael within hours. Dramatic images
OL,15,Fon the newswires showed explosions and
OL,16,Fdamaged buildings in Tel Aviv in the
OL,17,Ffirst few days of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
