OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThe volleys of missiles fired back and
OL,7,Fforth between Iran and Israel have
OL,8,Fcontinued, but visual evidence of the
OL,9,Fstrikes has become increasingly scarce.
OL,11,FWatch as ITV News captures Israeli
OL,12,Finterceptors chasing Iranian missiles
OL,13,Fbefore striking a skyscraper in Tel
OL,14,FAviv
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
