OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FEvery journalist and member of the
OL,7,Fpublic in Israel is subject to
OL,8,Fmilitary censorship, and the Israeli
OL,9,Fgovernment has the power to stop
OL,10,Fcertain information from being
OL,11,Fpublished or broadcast if it could
OL,12,Fharm national security - in short,
OL,13,Fanything Israel does not want Iran to
OL,14,Fsee.
OL,16,FIsrael does not want Tehran to know
OL,17,Fwhere its missile interceptors are
OL,18,Fstationed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
