OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThis means that while news
OL,7,Forganisations, including ITV News,
OL,8,Fhave camera crews in Israel, they are
OL,9,Fforbidden from broadcasting any images
OL,10,Fthat reveal the location of
OL,11,Finterceptor missiles or military sites
OL,12,Fhit by enemy projectiles - especially
OL,13,Fduring live broadcasts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
