OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIn Israel, there is an advanced
OL,7,Fwarning system for missiles being
OL,8,Faimed at the country, and news
OL,9,Fagencies, like the Associated Press,
OL,10,Fwhich works with ITV News and various
OL,11,Fother broadcasters, have to make
OL,12,Fefforts to change their live feed
OL,13,Ffootage to avoid breaking the rules.
OL,15,FIsraeli censorship focuses far more
OL,16,Fheavily on international media, and it
OL,17,Fhas tightened restrictions since the
OL,18,Fwar began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
