OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThe Israeli Defence Force (IDF) has a
OL,7,Fdedicated unit that posts and
OL,8,Fpublishes footage.
OL,10,FPlatforms like X, Telegram, WhatsApp,
OL,11,Fand Reddit can quickly become flooded
OL,12,Fwith videos claiming that huge strikes
OL,13,Fhave reached Tel Aviv or that IDF
OL,14,Fbases have been destroyed.
OL,16,FOften, these videos turn out to be
OL,17,Fmisleading or, with the continued
OL,18,Fintegration of AI into everyday life,
OL,19,Fplainly false.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
