OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIn order to verify social media
OL,7,Fcontent independently, news
OL,8,Forganisations check if the footage is
OL,9,Fgenuine.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FInternational news networks working in
OL,17,FIsrael do not submit every piece of
OL,18,Fvideo to military censorship for
OL,19,Freview, but censorship does prohibit
OL,20,Flive broadcasts of intercepts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/27
