OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIsraeli far-right Minister of National
OL,7,FSecurity Itamar Ben Gvir has turned
OL,8,Fthe apolitical military censor into a
OL,9,Ftalking point, vowing to "act with
OL,10,Fseverity and zero tolerance" against
OL,11,Finternational media that violate the
OL,12,Fcensorship rules.
OL,14,FIn a joint statement with the Minister
OL,15,Fof Communications, Ben Gvir said
OL,16,Fpolice have been dispatched to several
OL,17,Flocations as "suspects have been
OL,18,Fdetained, incidents investigated, and
OL,19,Feven arrests made in cases where
OL,20,Fsuspicion arises of violating the
OL,21,Fguidelines."
