OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,F"Anyone who endangers Israel's
OL,7,Fcitizens in the name of 'journalistic
OL,8,Freporting' will face a determined and
OL,9,Ftough police force," Ben Gvir said.
OL,10,F"No concessions, no games."
OL,12,FAnother thing to note is Israel's
OL,13,Fcensorship of satellite imagery.
OL,14,FTransmissions deemed a threat to
OL,15,Fnational security are blocked, and
OL,16,Fimaging software like Google Maps is
OL,17,Fblurred.
