OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FJust four hours after the first
OL,7,Fstrikes hit Tehran, a full internet
OL,8,Fblackout was enforced on the country,
OL,9,Fcurtailing information leaving Iran
OL,10,Fand cutting off Iranians from the
OL,11,Foutside world and each other.
OL,13,FThis is something that Iran regularly
OL,14,Fdoes for the regime to hold power.
OL,15,FDuring protests earlier this year and
OL,16,Fin 2022 following the death of 22-year-
OL,17,Fold Mahsa Amini, Iran cut access to
OL,18,Fthe internet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
