OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FTehran maintains strict regulation
OL,7,Fwhen it comes to internet censorship,
OL,8,Fwith the government and Islamic
OL,9,FRevolutionary Guard Corps consistently
OL,10,Fblocking social media such as
OL,11,FFacebook, X and Instagram to impede
OL,12,FIranian opposition.
OL,14,FFootage captures the moment a missile
OL,15,Fstrikes the side of the road in
OL,16,FBushehr, Iran - March 5
OL,18,FDespite the statewide ban, Iranian
OL,19,Fpoliticians sometimes use social media
OL,20,Fto communicate with their followers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
