OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FSome people have been able to access
OL,7,Fbanned sites using Virtual Private
OL,8,FNetworks (VPNs) and a limited number
OL,9,Fof Starlink satellites.
OL,11,FThis is how we have been able to see a
OL,12,Fsnapshot of life inside of Iran since
OL,13,Fthe war began.
OL,15,FIranian journalists working for ITV
OL,16,FNews in London have said that the
OL,17,Fstate's forced censorship has driven
OL,18,Fcommunity journalism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
