OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FSo the only way people can show the
OL,7,Fworld what is truly going on is by
OL,8,Fsending it themselves - despite
OL,9,Fpotentially fatal repercussions from
OL,10,Fthe state.
OL,12,FPunishments for breaching Iran's
OL,13,Fconstitution and freedom of expression
OL,14,Flaws range from fines to custodial
OL,15,Fsentences and the death penalty.
OL,17,FThe influx of UGC is then
OL,18,Findependently verified by journalists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
