OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThis all comes after decades of media
OL,7,Fcontrol and censorship by the Iranian
OL,8,Fstate.
OL,10,FThe state has such a stranglehold on
OL,11,Fthe media that back in 2024, Iranian
OL,12,Fjournalist Hossein Shanbehzadeh was
OL,13,Farrested and sentenced to 12 years in
OL,14,Fprison after replying with a single
OL,15,Fdot in response to a post on the
OL,16,Fsocial platform X by Iran's then
OL,17,Fsupreme leader, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,19,FIsraeli missiles hit the city of Bukan
OL,20,Fovernight on March 4
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
