OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIn an index compiled by Reporters
OL,7,FWithout Borders in 2024, Iran ranked
OL,8,F176 out of 180 in terms of the level
OL,9,Fof freedom of the press across the
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,FEven before the war, foreign
OL,13,Fjournalists had limited access to Iran
OL,14,Fand reporting from the country was
OL,15,Fgoverned by strict rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
