OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FCNN's Frederik Pleitgen and his team
OL,7,Fare among the few international
OL,8,Fjournalists reporting from within Iran
OL,9,Fsince February 28. Their access is
OL,10,Fsupervised and granted by the Iranian
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FWith all this in mind, it means that
OL,14,Fwhen using state footage provided by
OL,15,FIran, news organisations have to
OL,16,Fquestion its validity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
