OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIn Lebanon, strikes have been carried
OL,7,Fout against Hezbollah, an organisation
OL,8,Fdesignated by the UK as a proscribed
OL,9,Fterrorist organisation, after it
OL,10,Fattacked Israel in retaliation for
OL,11,Fstrikes on Iran.
OL,13,FThis Iranian-backed Shia militia group
OL,14,Fwas once considered the most powerful
OL,15,Fnon-state armed group in the Middle
OL,16,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
