OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FAs a result of heavy bombardment from
OL,7,Fthe IDF, much of southern Lebanon has
OL,8,Fbeen evacuated, leaving fewer people
OL,9,Fto film UGC and paving the way for Tel
OL,10,FAviv to document what is going on in
OL,11,Fthe country.
OL,13,FThe IDF has posted regularly and often
OL,14,Fabout the destruction in Lebanon and
OL,15,Fthe military targets it has destroyed.
OL,17,FBut in the capital, Beirut, people
OL,18,Fremain, and so do camera crews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/27
