OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FCrews monitoring the skyline of Beirut
OL,7,Fcaught IDF missiles wiping out an
OL,8,Fapartment building in the city
OL,10,FJournalists in Lebanon are also facing
OL,11,Frestrictions imposed by the pro-
OL,12,FIranian militia.
OL,14,FHezbollah has forbidden reporters from
OL,15,Ffreely accessing the militia's
OL,16,Fstronghold in Beirut's southern
OL,17,Fsuburbs, although they have organised
OL,18,Fdedicated press trips.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/27
