OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FGulf nations: Bahrain, Kuwait, Oman,
OL,7,FQatar, Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,8,FArab Emirates
OL,10,FAcross the Gulf states, some of the
OL,11,Fmost photographed cities in the world
OL,12,Fhave suddenly gone dark on social
OL,13,Fmedia.
OL,15,FHubs of trade, hotspots for tourism
OL,16,Fand a mainstay for influencers, you
OL,17,Fmay expect those living in the Gulf
OL,18,Fwould have greater freedom to post the
OL,19,Fdamage done by missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/27
