OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThe Gulf states are often seen as
OL,7,Ffortified powers with deep economic
OL,8,Fties to the US and, as such, have been
OL,9,Fdragged into the US-Israel war with
OL,10,FIran.
OL,12,FIn Bahrain, oil infrastructure was hit
OL,13,Fby Iranian missiles - footage ITV News
OL,14,Fwas able to source through various
OL,15,Fverification means and UGC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
