PN,31924
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FThe filming and sending of such
OL,7,Ffootage is now subject to
OL,8,Finvestigation from Bahrain's Cyber
OL,9,FCrime Directorate and considered by
OL,10,Fthe state as spreading fear and
OL,11,Fundermining public security.
OL,13,FIn Dubai, which is part of the United
OL,14,FArab Emirates (UAE), several people
OL,15,Fhave reportedly been arrested for
OL,16,Fbreaching the country's cybercrime
OL,17,Flaws.
OL,19,FThe UAE has warned tourists and expats
OL,20,Fthat they could face prison for
OL,21,Fposting material about the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
