OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FCEO of campaign group Detained in
OL,7,FDubai, Radha Stirling, said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "The UAE's cybercrime laws
OL,9,Fare some of the harshest in the world
OL,10,Fwhen it comes to social media. People
OL,11,Fcan face fines of up to USD 77,000
OL,12,Fsimply for posting commentary that
OL,13,Fauthorities say harms 'public order'
OL,14,For 'national unity'.
OL,16,F"In times of war, these laws become
OL,17,Feven more dangerous. Residents are
OL,18,Feffectively being warned to stay
OL,19,Fsilent online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
