CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773328289
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,F"We have dealt with numerous cases
OL,7,Fwhere foreign nationals faced
OL,8,Fdetention, travel bans or crippling
OL,9,Ffines over tweets, Facebook posts or
OL,10,FWhatsApp messages.. The risk is very
OL,11,Freal, and many people are now too
OL,12,Ffrightened to speak publicly, even if
OL,13,Fthey disagree with what is happening.
OL,15,F"It is illegal to take photos of
OL,16,Fgovernment buildings and people have
OL,17,Fbeen charged for posing in front of
OL,18,Fforbidden sites."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/27
