OL,3,CWhy are we seeing less footage from
OL,4,Csome countries during Iran war?
OL,6,FIt has also been reported that over
OL,7,F300 people have been arrested in Qatar
OL,8,Ffor circulating missile footage. It
OL,9,Ffollows an apparent spate of arrests
OL,10,Fin Bahrain and Kuwait for similar
OL,11,Fcharges.
